      "review_summary": "The PR changes main-session restart recovery to re-present the last user message for inspectable text-only assistant tails after gateway restart while keeping tool-call and approval tails on the fail-closed path.\n\nPR surface: Source +223, Tests +489. Total +712 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main source shows assistant tails take the unresumable resend/fail path, and source comparison shows the PR's new gate misses existing lowercase tool-call aliases used by transcript helpers.",
